          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Eula_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "優菈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "在護盾保護下時，該武器可以提供超高的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "加成，有效提升角色造成的傷害，適合隊伍中有護盾角色時的優菈使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 43,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Diluc_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "迪盧克",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "有護盾保護時，作為一把純面板武器，可以大幅度提高迪盧克的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "並提高生存能力。若護盾常駐，該武器的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "甚至比沒有特效時的狼末還高，很適合隊伍中有護盾角色時的迪盧克使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "辛焱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "辛焱作為自身能生成護盾的物理重擊輸出大劍角色，疊武器層數很快快，非常適合使用該武器。解鎖第二命之座後，還可以在元素爆發傷害結算前生成護盾讓武器加成效果翻倍，使元素爆發傷害更高。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 11,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Beidou_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "北斗",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "北斗的元素戰技可以生成護盾，觸發該武器的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "額外提高效果。同時北斗解鎖第一命之座後，元素爆發也能生成護盾，比較適合北斗使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
